Name: Average time from SW-Reviewer Declined to SW-AE Assign Reviewers
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Declined' and activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'

Name: Total time between SW-Reviewer Declined and the next occurrence of SW-Reviewer Agreed in the same case
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Declined' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Minimum time it takes to perform SW-AE Assign Reviewers after SW-Reviewer Declined
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Declined' and activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'

Name: Average waiting time to SW-Reviewer Declined following SW-AE Assign Reviewers
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Declined'

Name: Total resolution time of SW-Reviewer Declined measured as the duration between its timestamp and the subsequent reassignment activity (e.g., SW-AE Assign Reviewers or Assign a Different Editor)
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Declined' and activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'

Name: Elapsed time between SW-Reviewer Declined and Reviewer Invitation Reminder 1 when both occur in the same trace
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Declined' and activity 'Reviewer Invitation Reminder 1'

Name: Average time for the cycle starting at SW-AE Assign Reviewers and ending at SW-Reviewer Declined
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Declined'

Name: Minimum time between consecutive occurrences of SW-Reviewer Declined within the same case
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Declined' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Declined'

Name: Total time from SW-Reviewer Declined to SW-Reviewer Selection is now due when this sequence appears in a variant
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Declined' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Selection is now due'

Name: Time until SW-Reviewer Declined is performed after SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 3 days
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 3 days' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Declined'

Name: Average time it takes SW-Reviewer Declined to be followed by Unassign Reviewer
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Declined' and activity 'Unassign Reviewer'

Name: Total time between SW-Reviewer Declined and SW-Reviewer Unavailable when both appear in the same variant path
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Declined' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Unavailable'

Name: Minimum time from SW-Reviewer Declined to the next SW-Reviewer Agreed in variants that include multiple reviewer assignment attempts
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Declined' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Time of SW-Reviewer Declined relative to the initial SW-Initial Reviewer Selection in complex variants involving repeated declines
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Initial Reviewer Selection' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Declined'
